{"tid":1389882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醫渣出沒注意","createTime":"2019-07-31T04:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T05:57:36.000Z","uid":293871,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"09c40c91d0a4b3be0ed54798b3b6da757a253152","tid":1389882,"uid":293871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOi5bEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOi5bEC.jpg&h=1936000d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃金耀 - 瑪嘉烈骨科專科<br />\n普通科註冊編號 M07691<br />\n骨科註冊編號 S08-0133<br />\n<br />\n投訴及紀律研訊<br />\n對醫生作出投訴<br />\n投訴的程序<br />\n你可隨時與我們討論你的問題。若決定正式作出投訴，請盡量提供以下我們所需的資料：<br />\n<br />\n你的全名、地址和聯絡電話號碼。<br />\n有關醫生的全名和地址。<br />\n有關你認為醫生所犯錯誤的細節。<br />\n事發日期。<br />\n有關文件的副本以及例如錄音帶或相片等其他證據。<br />\n事件中可作證人者或任何可憑個人所知支持你所作投訴的人士的姓名和地址。<br />\n投訴信可以中文或英文書寫。你亦可選擇利用我們所載的這連結會以新視窗打開。表格作出投訴。<br />\n表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mchk.org.hk/tc_chi/complaint/files/complaint_form_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mchk.org.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomplaint%2Ffiles%2Fcomplaint_form_tc.pdf&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=4d617c74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mchk.org.hk/tc_chi/complaint/files/complaint_form_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n可致函或前往：<br />\n香港黃竹坑道99號<br />\n香港醫學專科學院賽馬會大樓4樓<br />\n醫務委員會秘書處<br />\n<br />\n你亦可致電2873 5131或2873 4853或以傳真2554 0577或電郵mchk@dh.gov.hk與我們聯絡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ns=595287177&amp;sfns=mo"},{"pid":"cb258e217481d693f0d57be35f10ddaf8f309492","tid":1389882,"uid":282834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc0eeb0914a48916c87d71158e9019112471d36","tid":1389882,"uid":163291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c0500dabeb79c89b53